QuestDescription.SourceString: Investigate the Garou and their rituals.
QuestDescription.LocalizedString: Investigate the Garou and their rituals.

Value.SourceString: Search Garou camps beneath giant wyrm bones in the Highlands for information on Garou ritual practices.
Value.LocalizedString: Search Garou camps beneath giant wyrm bones in the Highlands for information on Garou ritual practices.

Value.SourceString: Challenge a Garou king in their Highland stronghold and claim their token.
Value.LocalizedString: Challenge a Garou king in their Highland stronghold and claim their token.

Value.SourceString: Search garou camps beneath the giant wyrm bones in the Highlands for information on the King's Token.
Value.LocalizedString: Search garou camps beneath the giant wyrm bones in the Highlands for information on the King's Token.

Value.SourceString: Complete the ritual of purification on the King's Token at the ancient shrine where "a heart once beat".
Value.LocalizedString: Complete the ritual of purification on the King's Token at the ancient shrine where "a heart once beat".

Value.SourceString: Bring the Purified King's Token to Vannaka in the Ghornfell Highlands.
Value.LocalizedString: Bring the Purified King's Token to Vannaka in the Ghornfell Highlands.

Value.SourceString: Search the Ghornfell Highlands for a friendly face with an interest in Garou rituals.
Value.LocalizedString: Search the Ghornfell Highlands for a friendly face with an interest in Garou rituals.
